title: VonZipper : Weeman & Donavon Frankenreiter Shift Into Neutral
description: Truth be told, VZ has the hots for Mother Nature... So much in fact, we hug trees on a daily basis. It's with that embrace in mind; we're launching Shift Into Neutral -- a collection of sunglasses that are made from the environmentally friendly and sustainable materials.
